      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Linear-elastic isotropic constitutive model justified for Ti-6Al-4V below yield; contact modeled with augmented Lagrangian penalty; geometric nonlinearity enabled.",
      "rationale": "The linear-elastic isotropic model for Ti-6Al-4V is appropriate for pre-yield loading regimes relevant to stiffness and yield force QoIs. Contact between screw and vertebral body block is captured via augmented Lagrangian formulation. Geometric nonlinearity is enabled for the 40 mm displacement QoI, consistent with the physics of the test."
