      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus and Poisson ratio sourced from material certificates conforming to ASTM F136. Screw geometry digitized from CMM measurements with stated uncertainty. Input uncertainty was propagated through a 1000-sample Monte Carlo study, confirming QoI sensitivity to material variability is within acceptable bounds."
