      "rationale": "The assessment of test conditions was reviewed at a general level. ASTM F1717 protocol was followed and environmental controls were documented at both laboratories. Detailed gradation scoring was deferred pending consolidation of inter-laboratory environmental data; level assignment is pending final review."
