      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA boundary conditions mapped directly to F1717 fixture geometry; applied displacement rate matched; polyethylene block stiffness matched to measured compressive modulus.",
      "rationale": "Boundary conditions in the FEA replicate the F1717 test fixture geometry to within 0.1 mm. The displacement-controlled loading rate and fixture compliance are accounted for. The UHMWPE vertebral body block compressive modulus was measured and applied as a model input, ensuring equivalency between simulation and experiment."
    },
